{"segment_id": "mozi-046-preparation-against-a-sally__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0001", "section_id": "mozi-046-preparation-against-a-sally", "source_id": "mozi-046-preparation-against-a-sally__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 1, "text_original": "城百步一突門，突門各為窯灶，竇入門四五尺，為亓門上瓦屋，毋令水潦能入門中。", "text_normalized": "城百步一突門，突門各為窯灶，竇入門四五尺，為亓門上瓦屋，毋令水潦能入門中。", "canonical_ref": "46.1", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-046-preparation-against-a-sally__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0002", "section_id": "mozi-046-preparation-against-a-sally", "source_id": "mozi-046-preparation-against-a-sally__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 2, "text_original": "吏主塞突門，用車兩輪，以木束之，塗其上，維置突門內，使度門廣狹，令之入門中四五尺。", "text_normalized": "吏主塞突門，用車兩輪，以木束之，塗其上，維置突門內，使度門廣狹，令之入門中四五尺。", "canonical_ref": "46.2", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-046-preparation-against-a-sally__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0003", "section_id": "mozi-046-preparation-against-a-sally", "source_id": "mozi-046-preparation-against-a-sally__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 3, "text_original": "置窯灶，門旁為橐，充灶伏柴艾，寇即入，下輪而塞之。", "text_normalized": "置窯灶，門旁為橐，充灶伏柴艾，寇即入，下輪而塞之。", "canonical_ref": "46.3", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-046-preparation-against-a-sally__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0004", "section_id": "mozi-046-preparation-against-a-sally", "source_id": "mozi-046-preparation-against-a-sally__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 4, "text_original": "鼓橐而熏之。", "text_normalized": "鼓橐而熏之。", "canonical_ref": "46.4", "notes": ""}
